{"word":"G2556 - κακός - kakós - kak-os' - Bad","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κακός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kakós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kak-os'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bad"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கொடிய, பொல்லாத, பொல்லாப்புசெய்த, தீமைகளை அநுபவித்த, தகாத. கெடுதியான, தீங்கு அடைந்த, தீமைசெய்கிற, துர்க்கிரியையான, ஆகாத, துர்இச்சையான, துஷ்ட - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. of a bad nature"},{"paragraph":"2. wrong, wicked"},{"paragraph":"3. troublesome, injurious, pernicious, destructive, baneful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Apparently a primary word; <i>worthless</i> (<i>intrinsically</i> such; whereas <a href=\"#/G4190 - πονηρός - ponērós - pon-ay-ros'/4190\">G4190</a> properly refers to <i>effects</i>), that is, (subjectively) <i>depraved</i>, or (objectively) <i>injurious:</i> - bad, evil, harm, ill, noisome, wicked."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1573 - ἐκκακέω - ekkakéō - ek-kak-eh'-o/1573\">G1573</a>, <a href=\"#/G172 - ἄκακος - ákakos - ak'-ak-os/172\">G172</a>, <a href=\"#/G2549 - κακία - kakía - kak-ee'-ah/2549\">G2549</a>, <a href=\"#/G2550 - κακοήθεια - kakoḗtheia - kak-o-ay'-thi-ah/2550\">G2550</a>, <a href=\"#/G2554 - κακοποιέω - kakopoiéō - kak-op-oy-eh'-o/2554\">G2554</a>, <a href=\"#/G2555 - κακοποιός - kakopoiós - kak-op-oy-os'/2555\">G2555</a>, <a href=\"#/G2556 - κακός - kakós - kak-os'/2556\">G2556</a>, <a href=\"#/G2557 - κακοῦργος - kakoûrgos - kak-oor'-gos/2557\">G2557</a>, <a href=\"#/G420 - ἀνεξίκακος - anexíkakos - an-ex-ik'-ak-os/420\">G420</a>"}]}